<P style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt" class=MsoNormal><span style="COLOR: black; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold"><font size=3><span  style="font-family: Times New Roman;">Secretary of Defense Robert M. Gates hosts an honor cordon to welcome Russian Minister of Defense Anatoly Serdyukov to the Pentagon at 10 a.m. EDT.<span style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp; </span>The cordon will be held on the steps of the Pentagon River Entrance.<o:p></o:p></span></font></span></P>
<P style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt" class=MsoNormal><span style="COLOR: black; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold"><font size=3><span  style="font-family: Times New Roman;">Read On<span style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp; </span><o:p></o:p></span></font></span></P>
