<P style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt" class=MsoNormal><span size=3 style="font-family: Times New Roman;">Read On</span></P>
<P style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt" class=MsoNormal><A href="http://terrorism-online.blogspot.com/2010/08/army-casualties_31.html"><span size=3 style="font-family: Times New Roman;">http://terrorism-online.blogspot.com/2010/08/army-casualties_31.html</span></A></P>
<P style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt" class=MsoNormal><?xml:namespace prefix = o ns = "urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:office" /><o:p><span size=3 style="font-family: Times New Roman;">&nbsp;</span></o:p></P>
<P style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt" class=MsoNormal><span size=3 style="font-family: Times New Roman;">Biden Visits <?xml:namespace prefix = st1 ns = "urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:smarttags" /><st1:country-region w:st="on"><st1:place w:st="on">Iraq</st1:place></st1:country-region> to Mark Operation New Dawn</span></P>
<P style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt" class=MsoNormal><span size=3 style="font-family: Times New Roman;">While President Barack Obama travels today to <st1:City w:st="on">Fort Bliss</st1:City>, <st1:State w:st="on">Texas</st1:State>, and later gives an Oval Office address marking the end of combat operations in <st1:country-region w:st="on">Iraq</st1:country-region>, Vice President Joe Biden is in <st1:country-region w:st="on">Iraq</st1:country-region> meeting with <st1:country-region w:st="on">U.S.</st1:country-region> and Iraqi leaders about the new <st1:country-region w:st="on"><st1:place w:st="on">U.S.</st1:place></st1:country-region> mission there.</span></P>
<P style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt" class=MsoNormal><span size=3 style="font-family: Times New Roman;">Read On</span></P>
<P style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt" class=MsoNormal><A href="http://terrorism-online.blogspot.com/2010/08/biden-visits-iraq-to-mark-operation-new.html"><span size=3 style="font-family: Times New Roman;">http://terrorism-online.blogspot.com/2010/08/biden-visits-iraq-to-mark-operation-new.html</span></A></P>
<P style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt" class=MsoNormal><o:p><span size=3 style="font-family: Times New Roman;">&nbsp;</span></o:p></P>
<P style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt" class=MsoNormal><span size=3 style="font-family: Times New Roman;">Hurricane Season 2010: Tropical Storm Natheun (Western Pacific)</span></P>
<P style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt" class=MsoNormal><span size=3 style="font-family: Times New Roman;">NASA's Terra satellite flew over the <st1:place w:st="on">Northwestern Pacific Ocean</st1:place> at 10:30 p.m. EDT Aug. 30 and captured Tropical Storm Lionrock, Tropical Storm Namtheun, and Typhoon Kompasu in one incredible image. </span></P>
<P style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt" class=MsoNormal><span size=3 style="font-family: Times New Roman;">Read On</span></P>
<P style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt" class=MsoNormal><A href="http://talk-technology.blogspot.com/2010/08/hurricane-season-2010-tropical-storm.html"><span size=3 style="font-family: Times New Roman;">http://talk-technology.blogspot.com/2010/08/hurricane-season-2010-tropical-storm.html</span></A></P>
<P style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt" class=MsoNormal><o:p><span size=3 style="font-family: Times New Roman;">&nbsp;</span></o:p></P>
<P style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt" class=MsoNormal><span size=3 style="font-family: Times New Roman;">American Legion Honors Troops for Volunteerism</span></P>
<P style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt" class=MsoNormal><span size=3 style="font-family: Times New Roman;">Representatives from the five armed services were honored here today by the nation’s largest wartime veterans’ organization.</span></P>
<P style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt" class=MsoNormal><span size=3 style="font-family: Times New Roman;">Read On</span></P>
