<P style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt" class=MsoNormal><span size=3 style="font-family: Times New Roman;">Former <st1:City w:st="on"><st1:place w:st="on">El Paso</st1:place></st1:City> FBI Agent Sentenced for Federal Firearms Violations</span></P>
<P style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt" class=MsoNormal><span size=3 style="font-family: Times New Roman;">United States Attorney John E. Murphy announced that in <st1:place w:st="on"><st1:City w:st="on">El Paso</st1:City></st1:place> this morning, former Federal Bureau of Investigation special agent John Shipley was sentenced to two years in federal prison for violating federal firearms laws.</span></P>
