<P style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt" class=MsoNormal><span size=3 style="font-family: Times New Roman;">Iraqi Forces Arrest 2 Al-Qaida Suspects</span></P>
<P style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt" class=MsoNormal><span size=3 style="font-family: Times New Roman;">Iraqi security forces today arrested two suspected al-Qaida in <st1:country-region w:st="on">Iraq</st1:country-region> criminal associates during joint security operations conducted in east <st1:place w:st="on"><st1:City w:st="on">Mosul</st1:City>, <st1:country-region w:st="on">Iraq</st1:country-region></st1:place>.</span></P>
