<P style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt" class=MsoNormal><span size=3 style="font-family: Times New Roman;">Army Sgt. 1st Class Marc Seal returned here Aug. 13 from a five-day mission that began cloaked in secrecy.<span style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp; </span>The mission for Seal -- an infantry squad leader assigned to the Texas National Guard's agribusiness development team -- was known only to him and his command, and was kept secret for a special reason. </span></P>
