<P style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt" class=MsoNormal><span size=3 style="font-family: Times New Roman;">The special assistant for Integrated Undersea Warfare, Naval Mine and Anti-Submarine Warfare Command visited with residents at <st1:PlaceType w:st="on">Spring</st1:PlaceType> <st1:PlaceType w:st="on">Creek</st1:PlaceType> <st1:PlaceName w:st="on">Assisted</st1:PlaceName> <st1:PlaceName w:st="on">Living</st1:PlaceName> <st1:PlaceType w:st="on">Center</st1:PlaceType> in <st1:place w:st="on"><st1:City w:st="on">Boise</st1:City>, <st1:State w:st="on">Idaho</st1:State></st1:place> as part of Boise Navy Week Aug. 21.</span></P>
