<P style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt" class=MsoNormal><o:p><span size=3 style="font-family: Times New Roman;">&nbsp;</span></o:p></P>
<P style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt" class=MsoNormal><span size=3 style="font-family: Times New Roman;">Submariners Give Rare Glimpse Into 'Silent Service' </span></P>
<P style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt" class=MsoNormal><span size=3 style="font-family: Times New Roman;">On a recent sun-soaked morning hundreds of miles off <st1:State w:st="on"><st1:place w:st="on">Florida</st1:place></st1:State>'s Atlantic coast, this Trident ballistic missile submarine surfaced for an unusual operation. </span></P>
<P style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt" class=MsoNormal><span size=3 style="font-family: Times New Roman;">Read On </span></P>
<P style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt" class=MsoNormal><A href="http://military-online.blogspot.com/2010/08/submariners-give-rare-glimpse-into.html"><span color=#800080 size=3 style="font-family: Times New Roman;">http://military-online.blogspot.com/2010/08/submariners-give-rare-glimpse-into.html</span></A></P>
<P style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt" class=MsoNormal><o:p><span size=3 style="font-family: Times New Roman;">&nbsp;</span></o:p></P>
<P style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt" class=MsoNormal><span size=3 style="font-family: Times New Roman;">Authors in Corrections!</span></P>
<P style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt" class=MsoNormal><span size=3 style="font-family: Times New Roman;">Corrections, in general, refers to society's handling of persons after their conviction of a criminal offense.<span style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp; </span>For the Purposes of Police-Writers.com, corrections refers to all sworn personnel who work in prisons, jails, parole or probation functions; whether a local, state or federal facility.</span></P>
<P style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt" class=MsoNormal><span size=3 style="font-family: Times New Roman;">Read On </span></P>
