<P style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt" class=MsoNormal><span size=3 style="font-family: Times New Roman;">Veterans in the <st1:State w:st="on"><st1:place w:st="on">Gulf States</st1:place></st1:State> impacted by the recent oil spill may qualify for delayed mortgage payments if their mortgages already are guaranteed by the Department of Veterans Affairs. </span></P>
