<P style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt" class=MsoNormal><font size=3><span  style="font-family: Times New Roman;">Units assigned to Harry S. Truman Carrier Strike Group (CSG) rescued eight Iranian mariners in the <st1:place w:st="on">Arabian Sea</st1:place> Aug. 18.<o:p></o:p></span></font></P>
