<P style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt" class=MsoNormal><span size=3 style="font-family: Times New Roman;">Soldier Competes to Honor Late Wife </span></P>
<P style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt" class=MsoNormal><span size=3 style="font-family: Times New Roman;">The installation support unit safety officer here is competing in this year's Scottish Highland Games 2010 Masters World Championships in <st1:State w:st="on">Colorado</st1:State>'s <st1:place w:st="on">Rocky Mountains</st1:place> to honor the memory of his wife, who died in October.<span style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp; </span>"It gives me a way to keep my wife's heritage alive," Army Maj. Kenneth Knight said. "It's a way to stay close to her." </span></P>
