<P style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt" class=MsoNormal><span style="mso-ansi-language: EN" lang=EN><A href="http://policelink.monster.com/training/articles/144461-15-ways-to-spot-a-stolen-car"><span size=3 style="font-family: Times New Roman;">http://policelink.monster.com/training/articles/144461-15-ways-to-spot-a-stolen-car</span></A><o:p></o:p></span></P>
<P style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt" class=MsoNormal><span style="mso-ansi-language: EN" lang=EN><o:p><span size=3 style="font-family: Times New Roman;">&nbsp;</span></o:p></span></P>
<P style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt" class=MsoNormal><span size=3 style="font-family: Times New Roman;">Alaska Guard completes two missions, awarded 12 saves</span></P>
<P style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt" class=MsoNormal><span size=3 style="font-family: Times New Roman;">Members of the Alaska Air National Guard fought the ever-changing weather conditions in their state to complete two complicated rescue missions this week. </span></P>
