<P style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt" class=MsoNormal><span size=3 style="font-family: Times New Roman;">VA Nurse is Veterans' "Bridge" from Active Duty to Veteran </span></P>
<P style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt" class=MsoNormal><span size=3 style="font-family: Times New Roman;">Think "nurse" and you might think of syringes, blood pressure readings and thermometers. Not if you knew Brenda Stidham. She's an example of how the role of a nurse comes in many forms. </span></P>
<P style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt" class=MsoNormal><span size=3 style="font-family: Times New Roman;">Read On</span></P>
