<P style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt" class=MsoNormal><span size=3 style="font-family: Times New Roman;">Craft Talk</span></P>
<P style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt" class=MsoNormal><font size=3><span  style="font-family: Times New Roman;">One of the organizational principles of Rotary is the classification system.<span style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp; </span>That is, a Club should reflect the diversity of its local business environment by limiting the number of people from any industry.<span style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp; </span></span></font></P>
