<P style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt" class=MsoNormal><font size=3><span  style="font-family: Times New Roman;">Duckworth Takes to Skies Again <o:p></o:p></span></font></P>
<P style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt" class=MsoNormal><span size=3 style="font-family: Times New Roman;">Tammy Duckworth has achieved much since being wounded in 2004, but regaining her pilot's license has given the wounded warrior and top VA official a unique perspective on the control she has over her destiny. Gen. George S. Patton once said: "Success is how high you bounce when you hit the bottom." </span></P>
