<P style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt" class=MsoNormal><span size=3 style="font-family: Times New Roman;">These police officers turned authors have written true life stories about being a police officer on their department; or, in some cases a few departments.</span></P>
<P style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt" class=MsoNormal><span size=3 style="font-family: Times New Roman;">Read On</span></P>
<P style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt" class=MsoNormal><A href="http://www.police-writers.com/biographical.html"><span color=#800080 size=3 style="font-family: Times New Roman;">http://www.police-writers.com/biographical.html</span></A></P><BR/><BR><BR/><BR/>]]></content:encoded><comments>http://www.blogtalkradio.com/lawenforcement/blog/2010/08/03/american-heroes-press-top-stories-august-2-2010/#comments</comments><guid>http://www.blogtalkradio.com/lawenforcement/blog/2010/08/03/american-heroes-press-top-stories-august-2-2010</guid><pubDate>Tue, 03 Aug 2010 05:44:55 GMT</pubDate></item><item><title>American Heroes Press Top Stories August 1, 2010 - Aug 02,2010</title><link>http://www.blogtalkradio.com/lawenforcement/blog/2010/08/02/american-heroes-press-top-stories-august-1-2010</link><description><![CDATA[<P style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt" class=MsoNormal><span size=3 style="font-family: Times New Roman;">Army Casualties</span></P>
<P style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt" class=MsoNormal><span size=3 style="font-family: Times New Roman;">Read On </span></P>
<P style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt" class=MsoNormal><A href="http://terrorism-online.blogspot.com/2010/08/army-casualties.html"><span size=3 style="font-family: Times New Roman;">http://terrorism-online.blogspot.com/2010/08/army-casualties.html</span></A></P>
<P style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt" class=MsoNormal><?xml:namespace prefix = o ns = "urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:office" /><o:p><span size=3 style="font-family: Times New Roman;">&nbsp;</span></o:p></P>
<P style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt" class=MsoNormal><span size=3 style="font-family: Times New Roman;">Army Casualty</span></P>
<P style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt" class=MsoNormal><span size=3 style="font-family: Times New Roman;">Read On </span></P>
