<P style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt" class=MsoNormal><A href="http://leadership-online.blogspot.com/2010/07/logistics-analyst-excels-in-leadership.html"><span size=3 style="font-family: Times New Roman;">http://leadership-online.blogspot.com/2010/07/logistics-analyst-excels-in-leadership.html</span></A></P>
<P style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt" class=MsoNormal><o:p><span size=3 style="font-family: Times New Roman;">&nbsp;</span></o:p></P>
<P style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt" class=MsoNormal><span size=3 style="font-family: Times New Roman;">2400 Cop Books</span></P>
<P style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt" class=MsoNormal><font size=3><span  style="font-family: Times New Roman;">With the latest release of two novels by Lieutenant Wayne Zurl (ret.), Suffolk County Police Department, the website now lists over 2400 books written by state and local law enforcement officials, from 466 police departments.<span style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp; </span></span></font></P>
<P style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt" class=MsoNormal><span size=3 style="font-family: Times New Roman;">Read On</span></P>
<P style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt" class=MsoNormal><A href="http://criminal-justice-online.blogspot.com/2010/07/2400-cop-books.html"><span size=3 style="font-family: Times New Roman;">http://criminal-justice-online.blogspot.com/2010/07/2400-cop-books.html</span></A></P>
<P style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt" class=MsoNormal><o:p><span size=3 style="font-family: Times New Roman;">&nbsp;</span></o:p></P>
