<P style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt" class=MsoNormal><span style="COLOR: black"><font size=3><span  style="font-family: Times New Roman;">On July 29, 2010, Conversations with American Heroes at the Watering Hole will feature a conversation with Sergeant Brian Cain, Holly Springs Police Department, on marriage in law enforcement. <o:p></o:p></span></font></span></P>
