<P style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt" class=MsoNormal><span size=3 style="font-family: Times New Roman;">Fort Jackson Club Boss Puts Soldiers First </span></P>
<P style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt" class=MsoNormal><span size=3 style="font-family: Times New Roman;">Providing soldiers a home away from home has been Carole Coveney's mission for more than two decades. And Coveney will continue to take care of soldiers in her new position as the general manager of Fort Jackson's NCO Club. </span></P>
<P style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt" class=MsoNormal><span size=3 style="font-family: Times New Roman;">Read On</span></P>
