<P style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt" class=MsoNormal><o:p><span size=3 style="font-family: Times New Roman;">&nbsp;</span></o:p></P>
<P style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt" class=MsoNormal><span size=3 style="font-family: Times New Roman;">General's Son Pursues Same Path </span></P>
<P style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt" class=MsoNormal><span size=3 style="font-family: Times New Roman;">The O'Connor family from northwestern Ohio prides itself on spirituality and hard work, while giving back to their community. Army Brig. Gen. John "Jack" O'Connor, commanding general of Army Materiel Command Southwest Asia and director of logistics for 3rd Army, grew up in a tight-knit family as the youngest of six children. </span></P>
