<P style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt" class=MsoNormal><A href="http://military-online.blogspot.com/2010/07/mcpon-sends-2010-independence-day.html"><span size=3 style="font-family: Times New Roman;">http://military-online.blogspot.com/2010/07/mcpon-sends-2010-independence-day.html</span></A></P>
