<P style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt" class=MsoNormal><span size=3 style="font-family: Times New Roman;">Read On</span></P>
<P style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt" class=MsoNormal><A href="http://terrorism-online.blogspot.com/2010/06/threat-to-blow-up-fbi-building-in-dc.html"><span size=3 style="font-family: Times New Roman;">http://terrorism-online.blogspot.com/2010/06/threat-to-blow-up-fbi-building-in-dc.html</span></A></P>
