<P style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt" class=MsoNormal><o:p><span size=3 style="font-family: Times New Roman;">&nbsp;</span></o:p></P>
<P style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt" class=MsoNormal><span size=3 style="font-family: Times New Roman;">DOD to Implement New Suspicious Activity Reporting System </span></P>
<P style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt" class=MsoNormal><span size=3 style="font-family: Times New Roman;">The Department of Defense announced today that it will use the FBI-owned and maintained eGuardian suspicious activity reporting system as a long-term solution to ensure access to appropriate law enforcement related threat information in support of the department's missions. </span></P>
