<P style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt" class=MsoNormal><A href="http://criminal-justice-online-courses.blogspot.com/2010/05/massive-drug-trafficking-enterprise.html"><span size=3 style="font-family: Times New Roman;">http://criminal-justice-online-courses.blogspot.com/2010/05/massive-drug-trafficking-enterprise.html</span></A></P>
<P style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt" class=MsoNormal><o:p><span size=3 style="font-family: Times New Roman;">&nbsp;</span></o:p></P>
<P style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt" class=MsoNormal><span size=3 style="font-family: Times New Roman;">Army Forces Cyber Command Headquarters Standup Plan Announced </span></P>
<P style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt" class=MsoNormal><span size=3 style="font-family: Times New Roman;">May 21, 2010 - The Army announced today that it intends to establish a new Army Forces Cyber Command (ARFORCYBER) Headquarters within the National Capital Region, no later than October 2010. </span></P>
