iber Colt Dragoon or a .45 1911 Auto pistol-- they make an ORIGINAL DIRTY HARRY® for every handgun; to the exact handgun. They also manufacture the S.T.U. - the Severe Tactical Use shoulder holster - the hottest holster in the world; all leather and impervious to almost any element. Currently being sold to individual special operations personnel in Iraq. <BR/><BR/><a href='http://www.blogtalkradio.com/search/dirty-harry-holster/'>dirty harry holster</a><a href='http://www.blogtalkradio.com/rss/tag/dirty-harry-holster.rss'><img src='http://www.blogtalkradio.com/img/rss_tiny.gif' border='0' /></a><a href='itpc://www.blogtalkradio.com/rss/tag/dirty-harry-holster.rss'><img src='http://www.blogtalkradio.com/img/itunes_trans.png' border='0' /></a> | <a href='http://www.blogtalkradio.com/search/lawman-leather/'>lawman leather</a><a href='http://www.blogtalkradio.com/rss/tag/lawman-leather.rss'><img src='http://www.blogtalkradio.com/img/rss_tiny.gif' border='0' /></a><a href='itpc://www.blogtalkradio.com/rss/tag/lawman-leather.rss'><img src='http://www.blogtalkradio.com/img/itunes_trans.png' border='0' /></a> | <a href='http://www.blogtalkradio.com/search/jerry-ardolino/'>jerry ardolino</a><a href='http://www.blogtalkradio.com/rss/tag/jerry-ardolino.rss'><img src='http://www.blogtalkradio.com/img/rss_tiny.gif' border='0' /></a><a href='itpc://www.blogtalkradio.com/rss/tag/jerry-ardolino.rss'><img src='http://www.blogtalkradio.com/img/itunes_trans.png' border='0' /></a> | <a href='http://www.blogtalkradio.com/search/chicago-police-department/'>chicago police department</a><a href='http://www.blogtalkradio.com/rss/tag/chicago-police-department.rss'><img src='http://www.blogtalkradio.com/img/rss_tiny.gif' border='0' /></a><a href='itpc://www.blogtalkradio.com/rss/tag/chicago-police-department.rss'><img src='http://www.blogtalkradio.com/img/itunes_trans.png' border='0' /></a> | <a href='http://www.blogtalkradio.com/search/severe-tactical-use/'>severe tactical use</a><a href='ht