re. In that capacity he wrote news and news commentary, traveled in several countries interviewing top civilian and military personnel and taught “English as a Second Language” to Japanese high school teachers in night school. He also played dinner music on weekends at the Tokyo Plaza Hotel. <BR/><BR/><a href='http://www.blogtalkradio.com/search/police-chaplain/'>Police Chaplain</a><a href='http://www.blogtalkradio.com/rss/tag/police-chaplain.rss'><img src='http://www.blogtalkradio.com/img/rss_tiny.gif' border='0' /></a><a href='itpc://www.blogtalkradio.com/rss/tag/police-chaplain.rss'><img src='http://www.blogtalkradio.com/img/itunes_trans.png' border='0' /></a> | <a href='http://www.blogtalkradio.com/search/c-grant-wolf/'>C Grant Wolf</a><a href='http://www.blogtalkradio.com/rss/tag/c-grant-wolf.rss'><img src='http://www.blogtalkradio.com/img/rss_tiny.gif' border='0' /></a><a href='itpc://www.blogtalkradio.com/rss/tag/c-grant-wolf.rss'><img src='http://www.blogtalkradio.com/img/itunes_trans.png' border='0' /></a> | <a href='http://www.blogtalkradio.com/search/fellowship-of-christian-police-officers/'>Fellowship of Christian Police Officers</a><a href='http://www.blogtalkradio.com/rss/tag/fellowship-of-christian-police-officers.rss'><img src='http://www.blogtalkradio.com/img/rss_tiny.gif' border='0' /></a><a href='itpc://www.blogtalkradio.com/rss/tag/fellowship-of-christian-police-officers.rss'><img src='http://www.blogtalkradio.com/img/itunes_trans.png' border='0' /></a> | <a href='http://www.blogtalkradio.com/search/chattanooga-police-department/'>Chattanooga Police Department</a><a href='http://www.blogtalkradio.com/rss/tag/chattanooga-police-department.rss'><img src='http://www.blogtalkradio.com/img/rss_tiny.gif' border='0' /></a><a href='itpc://www.blogtalkradio.com/rss/tag/chattanooga-police-department.rss'><img src='http://www.blogtalkradio.com/img/itunes_trans.png' border='0' /></a> | <a href='http://www.blogtalkradio.com/search/police-officers/'>Police Off