<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt"><B style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal">About the Guest<o:p></o:p></B></P>
<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt"><A name=OLE_LINK4></A><A name=OLE_LINK3><SPAN style="mso-bookmark: OLE_LINK4">After completion of a </SPAN></A><A href="http://www.military-writers.com/united_states_marine_corps.html"><SPAN style="mso-bookmark: OLE_LINK3"><SPAN style="mso-bookmark: OLE_LINK4"><SPAN style="COLOR: windowtext; TEXT-DECORATION: none; text-underline: none">Marine Corps</SPAN></SPAN></SPAN></A><SPAN style="mso-bookmark: OLE_LINK3"><SPAN style="mso-bookmark: OLE_LINK4"> combat tour of duty in Iraq in 1991, Tracy E. Barnhart completed the National Registry requirements as an Emergency Medical Technician.<SPAN style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp; </SPAN>He responded to calls of emergency medical nature for over three years until he became a </SPAN></SPAN><A href="http://www.police-writers.com/"><SPAN style="mso-bookmark: OLE_LINK3"><SPAN style="mso-bookmark: OLE_LINK4"><SPAN style="COLOR: windowtext; TEXT-DECORATION: none; text-underline: none">police officer</SPAN></SPAN></SPAN></A><SPAN style="mso-bookmark: OLE_LINK3"><SPAN style="mso-bookmark: OLE_LINK4"> for the City of Galion (Ohio).<SPAN style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp; </SPAN>After three years on patrol he was promoted to the rank of Lieutenant. Later leaving the City of Galion Tracy E. Barnhart was hired as the Chief of Police for the City of Edison (Ohio).<SPAN style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp; </SPAN>After 3 years as chief of police, and with a total of ten years experience in </SPAN></SPAN><A href="http://www.hitechcj.com/enforcementfunction"><SPAN style="mso-bookmark: OLE_LINK3"><SPAN style="mso-bookmark: OLE_LINK4"><SPAN style="COLOR: windowtext; TEXT-DECORATION: none; text-underline: none">law enforcement</SPAN></SPAN></SPAN></A><SPAN style="mso-bookmark: OLE_LINK3"><SPAN style="mso-bookmark: OLE_LINK4"> he changed careers leaping into the realm of </SPAN></SPAN><A href="http://www.police-writers.com/corrections_writers.html"><SPAN style="mso-bookmark: OLE_LINK3"><SPAN style="mso-bookm