<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt"><a href="http://www.blogtalkradio.com/LawEnforcement/2009/06/06/World-War-II-Fighter-Pilot"><span style="color: windowtext; text-decoration: none; text-underline: none">http://www.blogtalkradio.com/LawEnforcement/2009/06/06/World-War-II-Fighter-Pilot</span></a></p>
