io.com/search/special-forces/'>special forces</a><a href='http://www.blogtalkradio.com/rss/tag/special-forces.rss'><img src='http://www.blogtalkradio.com/img/rss_tiny.gif' border='0' /></a><a href='itpc://www.blogtalkradio.com/rss/tag/special-forces.rss'><img src='http://www.blogtalkradio.com/img/itunes_trans.png' border='0' /></a> | <a href='http://www.blogtalkradio.com/search/war-on-terror/'>war on terror</a><a href='http://www.blogtalkradio.com/rss/tag/war-on-terror.rss'><img src='http://www.blogtalkradio.com/img/rss_tiny.gif' border='0' /></a><a href='itpc://www.blogtalkradio.com/rss/tag/war-on-terror.rss'><img src='http://www.blogtalkradio.com/img/itunes_trans.png' border='0' /></a> | <a href='http://www.blogtalkradio.com/search/afghanistan/'>afghanistan</a><a href='http://www.blogtalkradio.com/rss/tag/afghanistan.rss'><img src='http://www.blogtalkradio.com/img/rss_tiny.gif' border='0' /></a><a href='itpc://www.blogtalkradio.com/rss/tag/afghanistan.rss'><img src='http://www.blogtalkradio.com/img/itunes_trans.png' border='0' /></a> | <a href='http://www.blogtalkradio.com/search/united-states-army/'>united states army</a><a href='http://www.blogtalkradio.com/rss/tag/united-states-army.rss'><img src='http://www.blogtalkradio.com/img/rss_tiny.gif' border='0' /></a><a href='itpc://www.blogtalkradio.com/rss/tag/united-states-army.rss'><img src='http://www.blogtalkradio.com/img/itunes_trans.png' border='0' /></a>  <BR/><BR/>]]></content:encoded><category domain="http://www.blogtalkradio.com/">Military</category><comments>http://www.blogtalkradio.com/lawenforcement/2009/05/23/special-forces-soldiers-/#comments</comments><enclosure url="http://www.blogtalkradio.com/lawenforcement/2009/05/23/special-forces-soldiers-.mp3" length="14417630" type="audio/mpeg" /><guid>http://www.blogtalkradio.com/lawenforcement/2009/05/23/special-forces-soldiers-</guid><pubDate>Sat, 23 May 2009 04:00:00 GMT</pubDate><itunes:summary>On May 22, 2009, Conversations with Heroes at the Watering H